longBusinessSummary: PT Bank Aladin Syariah Tbk provides sharia banking products and services in Indonesia. It offers savings products, current accounts, and certificates; and funding and financing products, as well as other banking services comprising fund transfers, payments, purchases, and others. The company was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Jakarta Selatan, Indonesia. PT Bank Aladin Syariah Tbk operates as a subsidiary of PT Aladin Global Ventures.
